{
  "arquivo": "op_02_05",
  "total": 59,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, sorry to have kept you waiting.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Why are you here...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "To see you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "What are you doing?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "You shouldn't be here to meet me!\\nYou've always been thinking about that girl\\nand meeting her in Kyoto%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Um, well, that, just now...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What happened six years ago is irrelevant.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Th-that means...you really don't care about her anymore?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's not it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Huh...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'm still grateful to her for showing me the way back then. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "If it weren't for that meeting,\\nI would have continued to wander through life\\nwithout thinking about changing myself.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's pretty pathetic,\\nbut I always need someone to show me the way.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "For me now, that someone is you.\\nA person named 'Itsuki.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "For the past year and a half,\\nwhen I was unsure which direction to go,\\nyou showed me the way.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I want you to stay by my side from now on.\\nAnd%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I also want to become someone who can show you the way\\nwhen you're lost, Itsuki.\\nI want to be someone that you need.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I like you, Itsuki.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Huh...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Itsuki?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Itsuki.\\nWould you tell me how you feel?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's okay if you don't like me or just don't see me in that way.\\nI'm prepared for that answer as well.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...I don't know.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I don't dislike you.\\nI respect you as a friend.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "However...right now, for you...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...to say that...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "My heart is in so much pain, but it's not just\\nan unpleasant pain... There are also feelings...\\nthat are different from happiness...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "What...exactly are these feelings...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Itsuki...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "To begin with,\\nI don't even know what love feels like...\\nThat's why...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I can't answer you...here and now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...I see.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "However.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I don't want to run away from your feelings.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I know it's strange to ask you to strengthen your resolve.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "But please give me time.\\nI will definitely give you an answer.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...I understand.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "I'm sorry...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You don't have to apologize.\\nI've kept you waiting this long\\nto give my answer too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "And to top it off,\\nyour response...is just as unexpected.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Haha, I know.\\nI'm thinking the same thing.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's how difficult...of a problem this was.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "For sure,\\nwe both ended up tackling a tough problem.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "...Yes.\\nPlease just stay with me until I can answer, Sensei. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}